   5:			;
   6:			; OrgAsm v0.28 is 2-pass assembler for Sprinter computer that was created
   7:			; by Igor Zhadinets in late 2002 - early 2003. Source code of v0.28 was
   8:			; reverse-engineered back from binary v0.28beta and based on availavle
   9:			; source code of older version 0.15 (newer source codes were lost).
  10:			; Recreation work was done by Shaos <me@shaos.net> in December 2020.
  11:			; Most actual source code for OrgAsm will be always available on GitLab:
  12:			;
  13:			; https://gitlab.com/sprinter-computer/apps/-/tree/master/OrgAsm
  14:			;
  15:			; to build use this command: zmac orgasm.asm
  16:			
  17:			;Deb             equ 1           ;1 - асемблить отладочный код
  18:			                                ;0 - не асемблить
  19:			
  20:	4200          	Start           equ #4200
  21:	4000          	                org #4000
  22:			
